<paragraph blockId="30.[93,1049,1351,1662]" pageId="30" pageNumber="1545">Legs: Mid tarsus with a row of minute cuneiform setulae on posteroventral surface. Hind femur posteroventrally with about ve long setae; hind tibia ventrally with about 11 setae.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[93,1049,1351,1662]" pageId="30" pageNumber="1545">Sixth abdominal tergite tapering laterally, but reaching lateral margin of fth tergite, broadened dorsally.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[93,1049,1351,1662]" lastBlockId="31.[93,1050,654,756]" lastPageId="31" lastPageNumber="1546" pageId="30" pageNumber="1545">
